metadata.description: The QSkull Klan is a collection of 10,000 unique QSkull NFTs - unique digital collectibles living on the #Ethereum #Blockchain. Your QSkull doubles as your Klan membership card, and grants access to members-only benefits, the first of which is access to The Secret Room in our Web3 Site. Your  QSKull NFT  doubles as a pass for our  QSkullKlan Meeting Party , which will take place once a year, a mega fancy dress party where there will be fun. Visit www.Qskullklan.xyz for more details.
